author: Danielle Berjikian
description:
Despite Trump’s national efforts to make girls’ sports a thing again, many schools have done everything in their power to prevent that. Thus, the patriarchy prevails at one high school in Minnesota.

Marissa Rothenberger is a male high school pitcher in Brooklyn Park, and has been dominating female sports with a 12 percent hit rate against his pitches.

Meet "Marissa" Rothenberger, a 6-foot-tall MALE pitcher pretending to be a FEMALE, who has been dominating Girls' High School softball in Brooklyn Park, MN.

title: Male pitcher from Tim Walz's state is dominating girls' softball, but he says he's trans, so Democrats are ok with it
